title: FUBAR DiskFiller 2014 v1.1
description:
FUBAR DiskFiller 2014 v1.1
--------------------------

A little update, with a few fixes/upgrades:
- After setup, the application can disable UAC automatically. It will ask you if you wish that.
Disabling UAC gives the best result, by making this application run silently at logon and giving it Admin-rights.


--- OLD DESCRIPTION ---

Another version of this very annoying, and potentially harmful, application!

As usual:
- You will be given 2 warnings when you run this application. It is somewhat idiot-proof.


This one needs installation. Setup only takes a few seconds, and the application is ready to go!

Every time any user logs into Windows, this application will run.
It will fill up your harddisks (and connected USB-devices) with thousands and thousands of useless files!
More precisely: 10 files in EVERY folder, every time this application runs.
Each new file will be given a completely random name and size; ranging between 1KB to 7MB.

When this application runs, it will significantly slow down Windows, and it might take an hour or 2 for the application to finish.


Have fun!


/Ubehage
